snippet.title: [GOTY 2019 #3] Best VGM 2393 - A Short Hike - Somewhere In The Woods (Short Hike)
snippet.description:
OST: https://marksparling.bandcamp.com/album/a-short-hike-original-soundtrack

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC
A Short Hike (2019)
Somewhere In The Woods (Short Hike)
Mark Sparling
